abstract: >
  Code and documentation for a deployment-oriented evaluation of large
  language models for Arabic emotion classification. The repository covers
  zero-shot and few-shot inference, three-vote stochastic aggregation,
  run-to-run stability analysis, supervised Arabic encoder baselines, and
  pairwise McNemar significance testing.
